{"id": 2552, "title": "Ticket #2552: dollar dollar expansion break if shadows are reused", "description": "<blockquote>\nConfigure a personal condor with one slot.  Submit the following job\n\n<p></p><div class=\"code\">\n<pre class=\"code\">universe = vanilla\nexecutable = /bin/echo\narguments = $$(NAME)\n\nshould_transfer_files = never\n\noutput = o.$(PROCESS)\nerror  = e.$(PROCESS)\n\nnotification = error\nlog = log\n\nqueue\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>This should work fine.  Change the \"queue\" to \"queue 2\", and the second job will go on hold, unable to expand NAME.  If SHADOW_WORKLIFE is set to 0, the jobs will work again.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2011-Oct-17 14:09:34 by tstclair:</em> <br/>\n\nDoes this work fine in 7.6?\n\n<p></p><hr/>\n<em>2011-Oct-17 14:18:11 by gthain:</em> <br/>\n\nWorks fine in 7.6</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2011-Nov-14 12:47</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=28249\">[28249]</a></span>: move version history item to correct section of version history, and edit it. ===GT=== <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=2552\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('2552'); return false;\" title=\"dollar dollar expansion break if shadows are reused\">#2552</a></span>  (By Karen Miller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2011-Nov-09 16:46</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=28202\">[28202]</a></span>: Document dollar dollar problem <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=255